r948 | sam | 2006-05-09 15:52:15 +0000 (Tue, 09 May 2006) | 3 lines
Changed paths:
   M /libcaca/trunk/tools/makefont.c

  * Optimise similar glyphs when generating a font. Given how many glyphs
    are unavailable, this is a significant gain.

