  * libee/ee.h:
    + Got rid of ee_goto().
    + Moved <slang.h> or <curses.h> into libee.
  * Replaced ee_goto()/ee_putstr() pairs with ee_putstr().
  * Ditto for ee_putchar().

------------------------------------------------------------------------
